                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/phgy-459d1" class="program-course-title">
              PHGY 459D1 Physiology Seminar (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-33076" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Physiology (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/615">Faculty of Science</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Physiology              : Discussion of topics in mammalian, cellular and molecular physiology. Students will be required to write one essay and make at least one oral presentation per term. A final course essay is required.          </p>

